{"title_page": "Metropolitan University of Tirana", "text_new": "{{More citations needed|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox university\n|name = Metropolitan University of Tirana\n|native_name = Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiran\u00ebs\n|logo =\n|endowment =\n|image = Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiran\u00ebs.svg\n|image_size = 200px\n|latin_name =\n|established = 2011\n|type = [[Private University|Private]]\n|staff =\n|rector = Prof. Dr. Agim Selenica\n|faculty =\n|students =\n|city = [[Tirana]]\n|country = [[Albania]]\n|campus =\n|affiliations = [[University Iuav of Venice]], [[Frederick University]], [[University of Prizren]], London Trade Association<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.umt.edu.al/PunoMeNe/Partnere.aspx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-12-01 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031002930/http://www.umt.edu.al/PunoMeNe/Partnere.aspx |archivedate=2011-10-31 }}</ref>\n|colors =\n|website ={{URL|umt.edu.al}}\n}}\nThe '''Metropolitan University of Tirana''' ({{lang-sq|Universiteti Metropolitan i Tiran\u00ebs}}), abbreviated '''UMT''', is a [[private university]] located in [[Tirana]], [[Albania]]. It was founded in 2011, by a group of architects and engineers as the only Albanian university on [[information technology]], [[engineering]] and [[architecture]].\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of universities in Albania]]\n*[[List of colleges and universities]]\n*[[List of colleges and universities by country]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://umt.edu.al UMT official website]\n\n{{Universities in Albania}}\n\n{{coord|41.3202|19.8301|type:edu_region:AL|display=title}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Education in Tirana]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2011]]\n[[Category:2011 establishments in Albania]]\n[[Category:Universities in Albania]]\n", "text_old": "{{Refimprove|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox university\n|name = Metropolitan University of Tirana\n|native_name = Universiteti Metro